channel.desc: Makybe Diva, Australian Racehorse of the Year (2005, 2006) Australian Champion Stayer (2004, 2005, 2006) Australian Champion Filly and Mare (2005). Over $14M in prize money, 3 Melbourne Cups, nothing more to say - enjoy watching her run!
